Self.Wiki: This map object represents a generator within the map.

MaxNum.Wiki: The maximum number of enemies that this generator can generate in total.

GenType.Wiki: The spawn location behavior to use upon a generation interval.

LimitNum.Wiki: The maximum number of enemies that this generator can generate upon a generation interval.

MinGenNum.Wiki: The minimum number to use when determining the amount of enemies to generate within a generation interval.

MaxGenNum.Wiki: The maximum number to use when determining the amount of enemies to generate within a generation interval.

MinInterval.Wiki: The minimum time interval (in seconds) between each generation interval.

MaxInterval.Wiki: The maximum time interval (in seconds) between each generation interval.

InitialSpawnCount.Wiki: The initial number of enemies to spawn upon initialization of the generator.

SpawnPointNames.Wiki: The spot regions that the parts can appear at.

SpawnPartNames.Wiki: The spawned parts that can be selected.
